data.description: Beautiful 5 bed 3 bath move in ready home. An open concept design allows the space to flow from the great room to breakfast area and into the kitchen. The first floor also offers a guest bedroom and a Study.  The second story continues that open concept design by having a media area between the owner's suite and the additional three bedrooms. The secondary bedrooms offer abundance of space and most with enormous walk-in closets. The owner's suite offers a private bathroom retreat that includes large shower, dual sink vanities, private water closet, and a huge walk-in closet. Enjoy your nice patio with friends and family. With plenty of space for entertaining
